        "smartNation": {
            "title": "Smart Nation (2014 → Smart Nation 2.0 in 2024)",
            "paragraphs": [
                "Announced in 2014, Smart Nation aimed to use technology coherently across government, economy and society to improve daily life. Strategic National Projects like the National Digital Identity (Singpass) and national e-payments helped kickstart adoption at scale and set foundations for seamless digital services.",
                "On 1 October 2024, Singapore launched Smart Nation 2.0. The refreshed blueprint pivots around three goals — Growth, Community and Trust — to guide how technology is deployed for the next decade.",
                "Growth focuses on enabling people and enterprises to realise their potential with technology...",
                "Community emphasises inclusion and digital well-being...",
                "Trust strengthens security and resilience so people can use digital services with confidence..."
            ],
            "image": {
                "alt": "Smart Nation Vision",
                "caption": "Smart Nation connects digital government, economy, and society. In 2024, Smart Nation 2.0 refreshed the approach for Growth, Community and Trust.",
                "src": "assets/smartnation.png",
                "source": {
                    "text": "humanresourcesonline.net",
                    "url": "https://www.humanresourcesonline.net/singapore-launches-smart-nation-2-0-as-part-of-a-deeper-focus-on-digital-technology-investments"
                }
            },
