        "payments": {
            "title": "Digital Payments Surge",
            "paragraphs": [
                "The 2020s saw rapid growth in digital payments adoption. In 2020 alone, PayNow processed about 125 million transactions totalling S$22 billion.",
                "By 2022, transaction volume had grown to 311 million, with cross-border PayNow–PromptPay linkage enabling instant transfers with Thailand.",
                "Singapore launched SGQR in 2018 — the world’s first unified payment QR code — combining multiple payment schemes into a single label."
            ],
            "image": {
